com.datamelt.rules.core

Class ActionObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datamelt.rules.core.ActionObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ActionObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    a RuleObject identifies an object that will be instantiated and one of its methods will be run. The result will later in the process be compared to another value using a rule as defined in the respective rule definition xml file. RuleObjects are defined in xml files.
    Author:
    uwe geercken
